        {
            "title": "摩根士丹利調查顯示2026年IT預算預期略有改善",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pFGmgoQS.i.CBcZ9niF8ww--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPED3I0OT_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 摩根士丹利對首席資訊官的一項調查顯示,2026年科技支出前景略有改善,但整體情況仍然謹慎,且各類別之間的差異日益擴大。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師Keith Weiss在週四的報告中表示,首席資訊官顯示支出意向將從2025年的3.6%增長略微加速至2026年的3.7%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而,Weiss指出,\"預算趨勢看起來越來越呈現K型\",軟體推動了改善,而硬體、通訊和服務預計都將出現同比放緩。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a497e930-2bc6-3714-a14a-eb412b64e753-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">軟體預算預計在2026年增長4.1%,而硬體預計僅增長1.5%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">從地區來看,美國繼續超越歐洲,美國IT支出增長預期為3.9%,而歐盟為3.0%。美國的預期環比上調34點子,而歐洲首席資訊官則將其展望下調5點子,顯示出日益擴大的差異。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據稱情緒指標仍然好壞參半。Weiss表示,一年期上升與下降比率從2025年第四季度的0.5倍改善至0.8倍,但仍反映出淨謹慎立場,30%的首席資訊官預計預算減少,而24%預計增加。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在人工智慧方面,摩根士丹利發現AI/ML在首席資訊官優先事項清單上進一步上升,17.7%的受訪者將其列為首要優先事項,遠高於排名第二的安全類別的10.7%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">超大規模雲端服務商正成為AI錢包份額的早期贏家,微軟(Microsoft)和亞馬遜(Amazon)在一年期和三年期展望中均被列為增量IT預算份額的前兩大受益者。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%91%A9%E6%A0%B9%E5%A3%AB%E4%B8%B9%E5%88%A9%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA2026%E5%B9%B4it%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F%E7%95%A5%E6%9C%89%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84-155935059.html",
