        {
            "title": "TSX因地緣政治緊張局勢令停火前景蒙上陰影而小幅下跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pYSXPr7kqd_T5KPTyjagqw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/moved_LYNXNPEI2D0Y2_L.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 加拿大主要股指週四上午回落,投資者在脆弱的停火協議與能源市場重現波動之間權衡。截至美國東部時間上午10:28,S&amp;P/TSX綜合指數下跌150.94點或0.45%,而S&amp;P/TSX 60指數下跌8.66點至1,944.53點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次下跌發生在週三強勁上漲之後,當時市場因華盛頓與德黑蘭之間的外交突破消息而大幅反彈。然而,這項為期兩週協議出現的緊張跡象已削弱了最初的樂觀情緒,並促使市場對風險進行謹慎重估。</p><h3 class=\"mb-module-gap text-px20 font-bold lg:text-px18 text-batcave\"><strong>油價在海峽不確定性中反彈</strong></h3><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週四原油價格攀升,此前在上一交易日遭遇了自2020年4月以來最大單日跌幅。WTI原油期貨上漲7.86%至每桶101.83美元,而布蘭特原油期貨則回升至100美元關口附近。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-28f69eba-7b94-36fb-9437-d4b530072e82-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場參與者仍然關注霍爾木茲海峽,儘管敵對行動暫時停止,但該地區的交通仍然受阻。有報導稱,伊朗為回應持續的地區襲擊而停止了油輪通行,這使供應擔憂成為交易的焦點。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><h3 class=\"mb-module-gap text-px20 font-bold lg:text-px18 text-batcave\"><strong>通脹數據增加市場壓力</strong></h3><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管中東局勢發展主導了新聞頭條,但一批新的美國經濟數據提醒人們國內壓力依然存在。2月份個人消費支出(PCE)價格指數是聯準會偏好的通脹指標,年增率上升3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該讀數仍顯著高於央行2%的目標,顯示即使在最近的石油衝擊之前,價格壓力就已根深蒂固。投資者現在期待週五的消費者物價指數(CPI)報告,以更清楚地了解3月份的通脹走勢。</p><h3 class=\"mb-module-gap text-px20 font-bold lg:text-px18 text-batcave\"><strong>中東停火疑慮加深</strong></h3><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著德黑蘭指控違反本週早些時候斡旋的10點和平提案,外交局勢仍然不穩定。關於是否將黎巴嫩納入協議的分歧已成為各方之間的主要爭議點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管存在摩擦,伊朗談判代表預計將於週六上午前往伊斯蘭堡進行會談。美國總統唐納德·川普表示,美國軍隊將繼續駐紮在伊朗周邊,直到達成更永久性的協議。</p><h3 class=\"mb-module-gap text-px20 font-bold lg:text-px18 text-batcave\"><strong>黃金因避險需求而保持漲勢</strong></h3><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週四黃金價格繼續上漲,因地緣政治不確定性加劇促使投資者轉向傳統避險資產。截至上午中段,XAU/USD上漲近50美元至每盎司4,768.47美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此前,由於油價上漲引發了市場對聯準會將\"更長時間維持較高利率\"的預期,黃金曾面臨壓力。目前的轉變反映出市場重新轉向對沖中東衝突可能升級的風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/tsx%E5%9B%A0%E5%9C%B0%E7%B7%A3%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E7%B7%8A%E5%BC%B5%E5%B1%80%E5%8B%A2%E4%BB%A4%E5%81%9C%E7%81%AB%E5%89%8D%E6%99%AF%E8%92%99%E4%B8%8A%E9%99%B0%E5%BD%B1%E8%80%8C%E5%B0%8F%E5%B9%85%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C-154609653.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-10 00:11:33",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "軟體股遭拋售:Anthropic「Mythos」模型引發擔憂,PLTR、MSFT下跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Q6h6QwxW6sSH1MqrHXbmsg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA6U04V_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - Palantir Technologies (NYSE:PLTR) 週四下跌7%,軟體股在新AI產品發布以及做淡者Michael Burry對競爭威脅的評論後普遍下跌。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">iShares Expanded Tech-Software Sector ETF下跌3.7%,其主要持股包括<span><span><span><span>Palantir</span></span></span></span>、微軟(Microsoft)、甲骨文(Oracle)、Salesforce和Palo Alto Networks,均錄得下跌。此次拋售發生在Meta推出新人工智慧模型以及<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Anthropic\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Anthropic;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Anthropic\">Anthropic</a>發布用於構建代理的Claude工具之後。市場對Anthropic強大的新Mythos模型的持續擔憂也對該板塊造成影響。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d5fabf36-209d-3f29-993a-e8dd5c9ee07e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Burry特別強調Palantir面臨來自Anthropic的競爭威脅,他寫道:「Anthropic正在搶走$PLTR Palantir的生意。Anthropic的年度經常性收入從90億美元大幅增長至300億美元,是因為Anthropic為企業提供了更簡單、更便宜、更直觀的解決方案。PLTR可以專注政府業務,但那是低利潤率且規模較小的市場。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在Anthropic發布其Mythos模型後,軟體股所承受的壓力進一步加劇,該模型在軟體工程任務方面展現出顯著改進。根據Anthropic的系統卡,與之前的Opus 4.6模型相比,Mythos在Terminal Bench 2.0基準測試中提升了17個百分點,在SWE bench-verified基準測試中提升了13個百分點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Kotak Institutional Equities分析師Kawaljeet Saluja評論道:「Anthropic的Mythos模型在軟體工程任務的基準性能上展現出跳躍式提升,這與近期漸進式/溫和改進的軌跡有所不同。根據定性評估,Mythos在代理軟體開發方面提供了重大改進。我們認為,該模型對IT服務業構成近期至中期的顛覆風險,但需要注意的是,由於缺乏公開發布,該模型在實際場景中的能力基本上尚未得到驗證。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%BB%9F%E9%AB%94%E8%82%A1%E9%81%AD%E6%8B%8B%E5%94%AE-anthropic-mythos-%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E5%BC%95%E7%99%BC%E6%93%94%E6%86%82-pltr-152053411.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-10 00:11:35",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "哈塞特：川普有權依據緊急權力法對伊朗加徵關稅",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國總統川普的首席經濟顧問表示，川普有權依據一項緊急法律對伊朗相關商品徵收新關稅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">國家經濟委員會主任凱文·哈塞特周四表示，政府可以動用1977年的《國際緊急經濟權力法》，因為美國與伊朗「處於衝突狀態」。川普曾威脅對向伊朗提供武器的國家的商品徵收50%關稅。鑒於最高法院此前判定用《國際緊急經濟權力法》徵收關稅不合法理，此次他的關稅決定立即受到外界質疑。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「這顯然屬於總統的關稅權力範圍之內，」哈塞特在接受福克斯商業頻道採訪時說。「如果我們處於衝突狀態，那麼《國際緊急經濟權力法》的政策正是為此而設計的。所以各國確實應該謹慎。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-79895d76-072a-3188-a6e8-f1c187a3a83e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">如果川普通過引述這項緊急法律落實其關稅威脅，政府將面臨一場艱難的法律鬥爭，以說服法院認可其做法。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">白宮暫未回應置評請求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump May Impose Iran Tariff With Law Court Rejected, Aide Says</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
